{"tid":2441850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國擴大制裁緬甸軍方  敏昂萊兩兒子、旗下六間公司列入名單","createTime":"2021-03-11T03:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T04:57:01.000Z","uid":227801,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12b73e3e3d5a175ad5f4540873a76f660c4cad5a","tid":2441850,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"緬甸反軍事政變示威局面未見緩和，美國財政部宣布，將緬甸軍方領導人敏昂萊兩名兒子、以及他們旗下的六間公司列入制裁名單。聯合國安理會譴責針對緬甸示威者的暴力行為，並呼籲軍方克制，但在中俄反對下，未能就譴責軍事政變或採取進一步行動達成共識。路透社報道，緬甸保安部隊深夜在仰光兩個地區發射催淚彈與橡膠子彈，驅散示威者，並一度圍困數百人。有突破軍警封鎖的示威者表示，有人被扣押後遭到毆打。國際特赦組織批評，緬甸軍方正以戰爭用的武器及致命武力，去鎮壓自上月起反對政變的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-11 11:16:30<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579932-20210311.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579932-20210311.htm&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=d0157560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579932-20210311.htm&h=c62cfed4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579932-20210311.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd1b33f3e54b410a6870ad1f0a28ac5eaee51c98","tid":2441850,"uid":3241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfWy5EV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfWy5EV.jpg&h=cd52721c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n禍及妻兒了..."},{"pid":"1d2d25c22163ae1fa358d63faf6851e3588ecbd1","tid":2441850,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"幾時制裁林鄭兩個英國仔呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d82b105c238bb8422beb0d2a2961316bc0384e","tid":2441850,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28965ef9614e332374687426d7dda7621c6dc419","